%% AI Behavior Diagram
%% Purpose: visual overview of the bot/payload/test/dev interactions for developers and reviewers

flowchart LR
    User[User / Operator] -->|sends cmd| MainBot[Main Bot Controller]
    MainBot -->|request payload| PayloadGen[Payload Generator]
    PayloadGen --> Crypto[core.crypto]
    PayloadGen --> Obf[core.obfuscation]
    PayloadGen --> Dropper[Dropper / Payload Builder]
    Dropper -->|deliver| Telegram[Telegram API / Mock]
    Telegram -->|delivers update| PayloadBot[Payload Bot (deployed)]
    PayloadBot -->|executes| Target[Target Host / Sandbox]
    Tests[Tests & CI] -->|mock/validate| Telegram
    Dev[Developer] -->|run| Tests
    Dev -->|review| Docs[README / DEV_README / DIAGRAM]

    %% Optional flows
    Crypto -->|store key| KeyStore[Key Store]
    KeyStore -->|retrieve| PayloadBot
    MainBot -->|manage clients| ClientManager[core.client_manager]

    classDef infra fill:#f8f9fa,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px
    class Telegram,Tests,Dev,Docs,KeyStore,ClientManager infra
